        h2.header-1 How much storage do I need?
        p All CaseWare Engagement files are stored compressed via CloudSync. CaseWare Files compress up to 60% of their original size and therefore require less storage. A standard CaseWare engagement file, when compressed, requires less than 50MB of storage.

