    .col-sm-10.col-xs-12
        h2.header-1 How much bandwidth do I need?
        p Engagement files are transferred in compressed format. With the power of CloudSync technology, engagement files are only downloaded once to your local PC (or fully uploaded once to the Cloud) and thereafter only the changes made are synced between the Cloud and the local machine. This minimises bandwidth whilst always ensuring your files are up-to-date.

